---------------------minikube installation in ubuntu ----------------------------
	
1. downloade the package
   curl -LO https://storage.googleapis.com/minikube/releases/latest/minikube-linux-amd64

2. install minikube
   sudo install minikube-linux-amd64 /usr/local/bin/minikube

3. check the minikube version
   minikube version

4. start minikube in the top of docker
   minikube start --driver=docker

5. check minikube status it is running or not
   minikube status

6. display the clusters info
   kubectl cluster-info

7. display the config view
   kubectl config view

8. display the running nodes
   kubectl get nodes

9. display the pods
   kubectl get pods

10. open the dashboard of minikube on chrome
   minikube dashboard
